HEADWORD: Refringent
<hw>Re*frin"gent</hw> <pr>(-j<it>e</it>nt)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>refringens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>refringere</ets>. See
<er>Refract</er>.]</ety> <def>Pertaining to, or possessing, refringency;
refractive; refracting; <as>as, a <ex>refringent</ex> prism of
spar</as>.</def> <rj><au>Nichol.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
